  <brief_title>Effects of Immunosuppression on HCV Recurrence After Living Donor Liver Transplantation - Comparative Study Between Tacrolimus + MMF and Tacrolimus + Steroid</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Comparative Study on Effects of Immunosuppression on HCV Recurrence After Living Donor Liver Transplantation - Comparison Between Tacrolimus + MMF and Tacrolimus + Steroid</official_title>
