  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare immunosuppression protocol of tacrolimus + MMF with that
      of tacrolimus + steroid for preventing recurrence of hepatitis C after living donor liver
      transplantation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
